docs {
  # `POST` products
  
  ### description
   register a product to the inventory.
   when the product is created, creates a inventory transaction with `persons:undefined`.
  
  ### data body:
  ```ts
  //as json
  {
    mac_address: {
      type: string,
      address: string
    }[],
    product: string, // "products:id"
    serial: string
  }
  ```
  
  ### returns
   details of the created product.
   
  ### return model:
  ```ts
  ProductResponse: {
    data?: {
      id: string,
      mac_address: {
        type: string,
        address: string
      }[],
      product: {
        brand: string,
        id: string,
        model_name: string,
        product_name: string,
        type: string
      },
      transactions:{
        id: string
        type: string
        transaction_date: string
        user: {
          active: boolean
          created_at: string
          email: string
          fullName: string
          id: string
        }
        external_servide: {
          id: string,
          service: string,
          status: number
        }[]
      }[]
    },
    status: {
      code: number,
      description: string
    }
  }
  ```
  
  ### endpoint
  
  endpoint        | method | auth?
  ----------------|--------|------
  `/api/products` | POST   | true
}
